    "description": "<span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402380/extras/about_img.png?t=1699966569\" /></span><br><br>《过木不汪》是一款温馨治愈的解谜游戏。你将伴随小狗罗伯特，踏上一个寻找他梦中情“棍”的冒险旅程。<br><br>游戏玩法戏很简单：避开障碍物并规划一条通向终点的路径。注意了，这可没有你想的那么容易。还有，别忘了带着你的木棍！<br><br><br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402380/extras/features_img.png?t=1699966569\" /></span><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><strong>简单易懂的操作方式</strong> 通过移动、旋转、拾起或放下木棍来完成解谜.<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402380/extras/steam_01.gif?t=1699966569\" /></span><br><br></li><li>探索5个风格独特的地区，解决超过<strong>60</strong>个充满挑战和惊喜的谜题<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402380/extras/Steam_Landfill.gif?t=1699966569\" /></span><br><br></li><li>沉浸在一个精雕细琢的3D世界中，享受美妙动人的原声音乐。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402380/extras/steam_03.gif?t=1699966569\" /></span><br><br></li><li>- 通过插图，揭露狗狗罗伯托温馨感人的过去，探寻他执着于完美长棍的原因。<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2402380/extras/Steam_Story.gif?t=1699966569\" /></span></li></ul>",
